    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Foliation: Foliation in pencil, upper left recto (1-88, 84[a]-[147]); catchwords every verso, lower left.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Layout: 12 lines in two columns.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Script: Written in nastaʻlīq in black ink; pointed, partially vocalized.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Decoration: Remains of a headpiece in gold, red and blue with gold foliate marginal fill (f. 1v [adhered to upper board]); textblock and columns ruled in gold with second, faded blue rule around textblock; rubrications in red.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
      <subfield code="a">Binding: Pasteboard boards laid onto the top and bottom; wrapped in a damaged piece of unevenly cut brown leather.</subfield>
    </datafield>
    <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
